<component id="ID_txt16">
<text><![CDATA[Routers in this network are running auto-summarization. As a result, Router A and Router C both advertise the summary route 172.16.0.0/16. Router B receives both updates and installs both equal cost routes into the routing table. This causes reachability issues for both the 172.16.1.0 and 172.16.2.0 networks.]]></text>
